<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 pán shí pán shí yé sū jī dū chú nǐ yǐ wài bié wú jiù shú
 tiān xià rén jiān méi yǒu bié de míng wéi yǒu nǐ shì jiù shú zhǔ
 nǐ shì rén zi nǐ shì zhōng bǎo nǐ shì shén zi nǐ shì gāo yáng
 nǐ shì dào lù nǐ shì zhēn lǐ nǐ shì shēng mìng nǐ shì guāng
 yán shí shān zhài táo chéng dùn pái
 wǒ men shǔ yú nǐ yǒng bù yáo dòng zhí dào wàn dài</lyrics>
<title>pán shí pán shí yé sū jī dū 迦南77</title>
</song>